00:10:13.502 --> 00:10:15.268
hot zi vider gefast.

00:10:16.438 --> 00:10:18.693
far vos hot zi gefast nokh a kholem?

00:10:18.447 --> 00:10:22.508
far zi hot moyre gehat efsher vegn di kinder. zi iz geven zeyer frum.

00:10:22.648 --> 00:10:24.687
ANYTHING hot zi gedenkt s'vet s-

00:10:24.687 --> 00:10:25.916
s'vet epes ⟨HAPPEN⟩.

00:10:26.445 --> 00:10:28.396
hot zi a mol geredt fun dem?

00:10:28.622 --> 00:10:30.810
fun a kholem vos zi hot gehat?

00:10:30.968 --> 00:10:33.240
ver, do? do hob ikh gehat khaloymes.

00:10:32.841 --> 00:10:34.910
neyn, neyn, ikh meyn ayer mame.

00:10:37.515 --> 00:10:38.795
NO, m'hot nor gevust

00:10:38.795 --> 00:10:41.239
zi hot shoyn gehat a shlekht ⟨milkhome⟩, fast zi shoyn.

00:10:42.915 --> 00:10:45.862
un der tate, oykh geven a religyezer?

00:10:45.379 --> 00:10:46.402
OH, YEAH.

00:10:46.628 --> 00:10:48.765
er flegt leygn tfiln ale tog?

00:10:48.855 --> 00:10:51.262
NO, s- OH, SURE.

00:10:51.775 --> 00:10:54.030
