00:10:55.386 --> 00:10:57.287
yede zakh vos iz gekumen

00:10:58.440 --> 00:10:59.733
hobn zey gemakht.

00:10:59.925 --> 00:11:03.648
zayt ir geven noent mit di ale shvester un brider?

00:11:03.368 --> 00:11:04.206
vos?

00:11:03.823 --> 00:11:05.516
zayt ir geven noent

00:11:05.516 --> 00:11:08.086
mit di, mit di ale shvester un brider?

00:11:05.983 --> 00:11:08.778
mit hobn geleb- m'hot dokh gevoynt tsuzamen ale.

00:11:08.987 --> 00:11:10.938
ober ir zent

00:11:11.383 --> 00:11:14.769
ir hot zikh gut gefirt mit di ale shvester un brider?

00:11:13.611 --> 00:11:15.630
SURE, m'hot zikh gefirt gut.

00:11:15.855 --> 00:11:18.194
in di heym hot men gelebt gut. nisht do.

00:11:18.235 --> 00:11:22.616
ho- zent ir geven mer noent mit eyn shvester vi mit andere?

00:11:18.420 --> 00:11:19.544
do iz g-

00:11:22.555 --> 00:11:24.658
⟨iz⟩ geven mit ale noent THE SAME.

00:11:25.288 --> 00:11:26.885
