00:11:27.347 --> 00:11:30.868
dortn vu ir hot gevoynt, s'iz geven a yidisher gegnt?

00:11:30.891 --> 00:11:34.195
ye, vu undz- UNK di geslekh iz geven yidn

00:11:34.195 --> 00:11:37.601
nor di KOLEJOWA vos m'iz geganen arop tsu di koleyke

00:11:37.810 --> 00:11:39.964
zenen, veys vos meynt a koleyke?

00:11:40.088 --> 00:11:42.056
a koleyke heyst

00:11:42.383 --> 00:11:45.634
nisht keyn SUBWAY, nor dos fort ON THE TOP.

00:11:48.019 --> 00:11:49.155
az, az

00:11:48.053 --> 00:11:50.359
a, vi a ban, vi a STREETCAR.

00:11:49.155 --> 00:11:51.810
vi a ban, vi a ban. a ban.

00:11:51.951 --> 00:11:54.392
dos hot geheysn oyf poylish a koleyke.

00:11:54.904 --> 00:11:57.733
iz UNK geven geheysn di KOLEJOWer gas.

00:11:57.942 --> 00:12:00.005
a lange gas, azoy vi a

00:12:00.005 --> 00:12:01.094
BATHURST.

00:12:01.094 --> 00:12:02.452
nisht BATHURST nor

00:12:02.452 --> 00:12:03.943
a be- azoy

00:12:04.371 --> 00:12:06.474
UNK azoy vi BATHURST.

00:12:06.598 --> 00:12:10.712
dos iz geven, un di geslekh zenen mir aropgegan. dos iz geven di breyt di leng

00:12:10.712 --> 00:12:12.599
un di geslekh zenen geven

00:12:13.129 --> 00:12:17.454
iz geven KOLEJOWer, s'iz geven FRANCISZKANer, s'iz geven NALEWKes

00:12:17.454 --> 00:12:19.653
un dos iz alts farbrent gevorn

00:12:19.660 --> 00:12:21.682
ven zey hobn gevorfn di, di

00:12:21.682 --> 00:12:22.792
