00:12:22.984 --> 00:12:24.463
⟨fun⟩ bren shtof.

00:12:24.722 --> 00:12:27.326
hobn zey gevolt varfn oyfn GOVERNMENT

00:12:27.326 --> 00:12:30.465
iz nisht gefaln, nor s'iz gefaln oyf di ⟨dray STR-⟩

00:12:30.465 --> 00:12:32.782
geslekh. ale yidn hobn gevoynt.

00:12:33.261 --> 00:12:35.111
ven hot men zey gevorfn?

00:12:35.522 --> 00:12:37.372
