00:12:35.556 --> 00:12:39.392
vos? zey hobn gev- zey hobn gevorfn fun di AEROPLANES arop

00:12:38.188 --> 00:12:39.498
ven? ven?

00:12:39.392 --> 00:12:41.506
azoy vi di krig hot zikh ge- ongehoybn.

00:12:41.057 --> 00:12:42.958
ah, nayn un draysikstn yor.

00:12:42.289 --> 00:12:44.783
yo, bald, hobn zey bald gevorfn

00:12:44.783 --> 00:12:49.539
un undz ho'mir shoyn nisht gehat vu tsu voynen. m'hot nor gehat dem STORE, eyn sh- eyn groyse shtub.

00:12:49.782 --> 00:12:52.391
m'hot undz arayngezetst vu mentshn voynen.

00:12:52.566 --> 00:12:55.212
iz zey hobn zikh mit undz gevorfn, az zey

00:12:55.212 --> 00:12:57.825
s'iz zey gelungen, zenen nisht farbrent gevorn

00:12:58.067 --> 00:13:03.697
hobn zikh gevorfn mit di mentshn vos se, zey hobn geblibn on, on PLACE tsu, vu tsu voynen.

00:13:05.560 --> 00:13:07.612
ir gedenkt ayere shkheynim?

