oyf FRANCISZKANSKA?

00:13:10.723 --> 00:13:13.113
zol ikh zogn, zol ikh zogn di nemen?

00:13:13.018 --> 00:13:14.294
ir gedenkt zey?

00:13:14.098 --> 00:13:17.686
ye. Khayele UNK. zi hot gemakht sheytlen

00:13:18.148 --> 00:13:20.760
iz geven nisht vayt fun undz azoy

00:13:20.760 --> 00:13:22.192
⟨zi⟩ opgerukt

00:13:22.620 --> 00:13:24.318
Khaye di UNK

00:13:25.489 --> 00:13:27.187
Hinde Tsipes

00:13:28.206 --> 00:13:30.798
dos iz gevezn eyn hoyz

00:13:31.918 --> 00:13:33.684
yetst iz gevezn

00:13:34.298 --> 00:13:37.937
un a tsveyte PLACE, di nemen fun di mentshn?

00:13:37.673 --> 00:13:38.598
neyn, a-

00:13:38.598 --> 00:13:40.029
oyb ir gedenkt zey.

00:13:39.613 --> 00:13:41.531
Sheyndl UNK

00:13:42.027 --> 00:13:43.928
zi iz geven eyne, nor

00:13:44.322 --> 00:13:46.529
zol ikh ⟨oyfgeyn⟩? Gitl Rivke Moyshes

00:13:46.529 --> 00:13:48.500
⟨iz zi⟩ gegan in di hayzer nor

00:13:48.861 --> 00:13:51.369
zol ikh dos oyf⟨UNK⟩? NO, dos nisht.

00:13:51.443 --> 00:13:53.529
s'iz geven Yitskhok ⟨LOFTSHIK⟩

00:13:54.767 --> 00:13:56.550
Meyer GLATSHTEYN

00:13:58.142 --> 00:13:59.536
iz gevezn

00:14:00.150 --> 00:14:02.034
s'iz geven undzer gesl.

00:14:02.817 --> 00:14:05.595
di tsveyte iz geven Ester Rivke.

00:14:07.558 --> 00:14:08.750
do iz geven

00:14:08.773 --> 00:14:12.159
Pintshe DEMBROVSKI. efsher hostu gehat gehert fun im? NO.

00:14:12.925 --> 00:14:14.606
un s'iz gevezn

00:14:16.929 --> 00:14:18.757
Simkhe ⟨di bekerin⟩

00:14:20.400 --> 00:14:22.453
un vos nokh iz gevezn?

00:14:24.822 --> 00:14:26.858
