00:14:27.420 --> 00:14:31.987
UNK di SCHOOL zenen dokh geganen, UNK nokh yung. in di SCHOOL zenen mir geven

00:14:32.145 --> 00:14:34.788
vos far a frage? m'iz gan in SCHOOL un m'hot gehat

00:14:34.896 --> 00:14:36.324
⟨KRIKSHTEYN⟩

00:14:36.887 --> 00:14:38.923
tsvey shvestern geven.

00:14:38.490 --> 00:14:41.116
ikh hob gemeynt, tsi zaynen zey geven ale yidn?

00:14:41.427 --> 00:14:43.733
oh, di vos ikh zog zenen ale yidn.

00:14:43.502 --> 00:14:45.330
neyn, ober di fraynt ayere.

00:14:45.330 --> 00:14:47.849
hot ir gehat goyishe fraynt?

00:14:46.438 --> 00:14:50.094
ye, ⟨KRIKSHTEYNS⟩, NO, UNK iz nor gekumen in SCHOOL arayn.

00:14:50.134 --> 00:14:52.237
m'hot gehat ⟨KRIKSHTEYN⟩ fraynt.

00:14:52.243 --> 00:14:55.797
s'iz gevezn Shifre ⟨SOLARZ⟩ iz gevezn

00:14:55.922 --> 00:14:59.134
⟨MILGROM⟩. dos iz geven ⟨CLOSE⟩ fun di SCHOOL.

00:14:59.134 --> 00:15:00.574
di yidishe fraynt.

00:15:00.698 --> 00:15:03.932
un azoy di goyim zenen tsunoyfgekumen in SCHOOL arayn.

00:15:04.613 --> 00:15:07.965
