00:15:37.789 --> 00:15:40.279
⟨ven⟩ m'iz aroysgegan di yidishe meydlekh.

00:15:40.279 --> 00:15:41.909
d- kinder, yungen.

00:15:41.909 --> 00:15:44.021
hobn zey ongehoybn tsu tshepen. nakher

00:15:44.021 --> 00:15:46.350
hobn zey ongehoybn, geven a tume gas

00:15:46.350 --> 00:15:49.376
