00:16:01.735 --> 00:16:03.484
ver s'hot balangt tsu zey

00:16:03.523 --> 00:16:06.895
hobn zey ongehoybn tsu shlogn zey. zey hobn ranirt

00:16:06.895 --> 00:16:09.098
a sakh BOYS hobn zey ranirt.

00:16:11.505 --> 00:16:13.136
dos iz di krig hot zikh ongehoybn.

00:16:14.340 --> 00:16:17.366
azoy iz geven shtil. azoy vi m'hot zey UNK

00:16:17.366 --> 00:16:18.705
organizirn

00:16:19.032 --> 00:16:20.747
zenen zey shoyn gevorn

00:16:20.770 --> 00:16:22.131
oyfgeklert

00:16:22.204 --> 00:16:25.117
az di yidn zenen BUSINESS un raykh

00:16:25.174 --> 00:16:27.668
