00:18:20.667 --> 00:18:23.170
UND di shvester gedenk ikh ⟨dokh⟩ nisht.

00:18:23.299 --> 00:18:25.149
UNK zi hot dokh do kinder.

00:18:25.341 --> 00:18:26.772
