00:20:57.368 --> 00:20:59.879
in STORE, di CUSTOMERS in mark.

00:20:59.879 --> 00:21:02.289
m'hot gekoyft bay zey, az zey hob gebrengt

00:21:02.397 --> 00:21:04.376
tvue, veyst ⟨vos⟩ meynt tvue?

00:21:04.376 --> 00:21:08.162
gebrengt eyer, hiner. m'hot geredt mit zey ale poylish.

00:21:08.539 --> 00:21:11.599
in hoyz zenen arayngekumen CUSTOMERS poylish

00:21:11.599 --> 00:21:14.679
zol araynkumen yidish, hot men geredt yidish, nisht ken poylish

00:21:15.205 --> 00:21:17.679
s'iz nisht azoy vi do, me redt poylish

00:21:17.702 --> 00:21:18.911
poylish.

00:21:20.622 --> 00:21:25.037
kent ir mir bashraybn a shabes, vi s'iz geven oyf a shabes?

00:21:25.026 --> 00:21:26.150
in di heym?

00:21:27.355 --> 00:21:31.736
fraytik tsu nakhts, m'hot ongetsundn di vay- geleygt di vayse tishtekher

00:21:31.928 --> 00:21:37.626
mit di likht hobn gebrent UNK mit di likht es ge- ongeputst di likht, es hobn ⟨geshpiglt⟩

00:21:38.695 --> 00:21:41.237
un, un foter geganen tsum davenen.

00:21:42.492 --> 00:21:45.186
undz kinder zenen mir nokh gelofn in gortn arayn

00:21:45.377 --> 00:21:48.965
ober m'hot gedenkt az me darf tsuriktsukumen, me zol zayn tsu di TIME

00:21:48.972 --> 00:21:52.374
nisht geshlogn, nor di respekt farn tish.

00:21:52.937 --> 00:21:54.832
nu, hot gemakht kidesh

00:21:54.832 --> 00:21:56.694
di brider, mayn ⟨tateshi⟩.

00:21:56.987 --> 00:21:58.587
es iz geven fish.

00:21:58.587 --> 00:22:00.846
s'iz geven alding, nisht azoy vi do.

00:22:01.105 --> 00:22:03.174
do geyt men in di restoranen.

00:22:03.298 --> 00:22:05.151
me g- khapt a SANDWICH.

00:22:05.151 --> 00:22:07.207
in di heym iz geven, in di heym.

00:22:07.990 --> 00:22:08.979
dayn ma-

00:22:08.007 --> 00:22:12.743
ober do, ober do kon men makhn a beser lebn. in di heym iz nisht geven vu tsu arbetn.

00:22:13.052 --> 00:22:16.623
in a kleyn shtetl hot men nisht gehat vos tsu tun a mentsh.

00:22:16.680 --> 00:22:19.694
di mame hot alts tsugegreyt, alts gekokht aleyn?

00:22:19.195 --> 00:22:20.724
NO, ze- zi

00:22:20.983 --> 00:22:24.892
zi iz nisht geven feik. zi iz geven di beste shnayderin in di shtot

00:22:24.983 --> 00:22:27.272
fun DRESSES. zi hot getun.

00:22:27.497 --> 00:22:29.668
ober mayn shvester fun NEW YORK

00:22:29.708 --> 00:22:31.018
hot MOST geholfn.

00:22:31.075 --> 00:22:33.111
BEGINNING hot zi gehat a MAID.

00:22:33.606 --> 00:22:38.207
shpeter, di kinder hobn ongehoybn a bisl greser tsu vern, hot yeder geholfn epes.

00:22:37.572 --> 00:22:38.730
tsu kokhn.

00:22:38.837 --> 00:22:40.889
nu, tsu kokhn, tsutsugreytn.

00:22:38.905 --> 00:22:40.299
tsutsugreytn.

00:22:40.963 --> 00:22:42.476
kokhn hot zi gekokht.

00:22:42.178 --> 00:22:43.640
vos hot ir geton?

00:22:44.068 --> 00:22:44.787
vos?

00:22:44.372 --> 00:22:46.087
vos hot ir geton aleyn?

00:22:46.380 --> 00:22:47.876
vos ikh hob getun?

00:22:48.557 --> 00:22:52.230
bin dokh gan in SCHOOL arayn, nokh a por yor UNK gan in SCHOOL arayn

00:22:52.860 --> 00:22:56.988
vi lang hot genumen di krig. eyder m'hot zikh oysgedreyt iz gevorn di krig.

00:22:57.197 --> 00:22:58.558
vos hot men UNK

00:22:57.231 --> 00:23:00.397
vi alt zent ir geven ven di krig hot zikh ongehoybn?

00:23:00.673 --> 00:23:05.611
veyst ikh bin alt yetst NINETEEN TWENTY ONE. vifl ⟨ir vet rekhenen dos⟩ etlekhe un fuftsik yor.

00:23:05.668 --> 00:23:07.248
iz shoyn nokh di krig.

00:23:07.575 --> 00:23:11.686
m'iz gegan in di krig arayn. ikh bin gevezn finef yor in di krig.

00:23:12.233 --> 00:23:13.647
bin geven genug yung.

00:23:13.647 --> 00:23:14.659
genug ⟨az ikh hob⟩

00:23:14.659 --> 00:23:15.922
adurkhgemakht

00:23:16.502 --> 00:23:18.251
azelekhe tsores

00:23:19.017 --> 00:23:22.099
oyb es volt gekumen nokh a krig, vel ikh shoyn nisht lebn

00:23:22.678 --> 00:23:24.764
vos undz hot men adurkhgemakht.

00:23:26.458 --> 00:23:29.034
dos iz nisht tsu bashraybn in di BOOKS.

00:23:29.310 --> 00:23:31.666
az zey shraybn a TEMAT

00:23:31.740 --> 00:23:33.067
veyst a TEMAT?

00:23:33.546 --> 00:23:35.059
a PROJECT

00:23:35.233 --> 00:23:36.256
TEMAT oyf po-

00:23:36.364 --> 00:23:38.737
MOST khap ikh aroys poylishe verter.

00:23:38.760 --> 00:23:40.205
bin ⟨tsugetrayt⟩

00:23:40.617 --> 00:23:45.488
shraybt men dokh nisht di gantse historye fun di BOOK. me nemt aroys epes fun yede

00:23:45.595 --> 00:23:46.736
bletl.

00:23:47.518 --> 00:23:51.916
un vos konstu shraybn alding? UNK shraybn dokh gornisht fun dem

00:23:52.260 --> 00:23:53.503
vos iz gevezn.

00:23:56.293 --> 00:23:58.345
s'iz geven BAD, THE LIFE.

00:23:59.213 --> 00:24:01.485
vi iz es geven peysekh tsayt?

00:24:01.474 --> 00:24:05.248
oh, peysekh, hot men ongerikht a seyder, OH BOY.

00:24:06.351 --> 00:24:09.112
nu, nor do hot men oykh shoyn gerikht a seyder.

00:24:09.253 --> 00:24:10.934
dertseylt mir fun dortn.

00:24:11.143 --> 00:24:12.251
dortn

00:24:12.814 --> 00:24:15.153
avekgeshtelt a teler mit eyer

00:24:15.953 --> 00:24:17.617
teler zalts vaser

00:24:17.893 --> 00:24:19.169
mit zalts

00:24:19.851 --> 00:24:21.093
un

00:24:21.100 --> 00:24:24.705
lekhaim avekgeshtelt. alts UNK shoyn geven servirt

00:24:24.913 --> 00:24:26.274
a gantse leng.

00:24:26.297 --> 00:24:28.653
UNK geven akht mentshn tsum esn.

00:24:29.436 --> 00:24:31.390
der bruder iz shoyn geven der

00:24:31.390 --> 00:24:33.682
STEP BROTHER iz shoyn geven in Tshenstekhev.

00:24:33.773 --> 00:24:36.993
zenen mir undz geven akht mentshn. ⟨s'iz nokh⟩ geven a khasene tsu makhn

00:24:36.993 --> 00:24:38.121
akht mentshn.

00:24:39.308 --> 00:24:42.407
ikh hob nisht, ikh hob nisht geglikhn keyn geroysh.

00:24:42.767 --> 00:24:46.068
shoyn yeder hot epes geredt, iz shoyn geven a geroysh.

00:24:46.783 --> 00:24:49.291
I DON'T LIKE TOO MUCH NOISE.

00:24:51.559 --> 00:24:55.080
un kartofl hot men dokh gemuzt hobn tsum zalts vaser.

00:24:56.352 --> 00:24:59.468
BREAD UNK ⟨oyfgeven⟩ biz tsveye bay di nakht.

00:24:59.997 --> 00:25:03.585
un mayn ⟨tateshi⟩ hot gekont zeyer sheyn zingen, mayn bruder.

00:25:03.979 --> 00:25:06.723
s'hot, s'hot geklungen di, di gas

00:25:06.882 --> 00:25:08.681
vi zey hobn ongerikht a seyder.

00:25:09.261 --> 00:25:11.567
hot ir a mol gehat gest tsum seyder?

00:25:12.096 --> 00:25:14.553
NO, in di heym iz nisht geven ⟨aza STYLE⟩.

00:25:14.577 --> 00:25:17.560
vos mit shabes tsayt? hot ir a mol ayngeladn

00:25:17.560 --> 00:25:18.941
oreme layt?

00:25:17.648 --> 00:25:19.045
s'iz nisht geve-

00:25:19.045 --> 00:25:21.694
oh, mayn ⟨tateshi⟩ iz ge- balangt tsu

00:25:21.694 --> 00:25:23.581
a besmedresh hot es geheysn.

00:25:23.638 --> 00:25:26.332
hot men ⟨yeder⟩ shabes gegebn an oreman.

00:25:27.030 --> 00:25:28.711
es zenen nokh geven oreme layt

00:25:29.342 --> 00:25:31.327
nokh gemuzt aroysnemen hilf.

00:25:32.565 --> 00:25:34.989
zenen zey ale mol geven andere mentshn?

00:25:35.097 --> 00:25:38.519
tsveyte, tsveyte zenen gekumen tsu forn in tsveyte shtetl

00:25:38.519 --> 00:25:41.216
zenen dokh arumgeforn nokh a protsent makhn.

00:25:41.391 --> 00:25:44.574
nu, zenen zey arayngan in di shul arayn tsi in besmedresh

00:25:44.614 --> 00:25:48.084
un der RABBI hot shoyn tseteylt zey ver es nemt aheym.

00:25:48.698 --> 00:25:50.396
m'iz shtendik ⟨aheymganen⟩.

00:25:51.043 --> 00:25:53.905
a mentsh tsu esn fraytik tsu nakhts un shabes

00:25:54.250 --> 00:25:59.627
gedenkt ir vi azoy ir hot reagirt als meydl az ir hot gezen fremde in hoyz?

00:26:00.223 --> 00:26:02.579
m'iz gezitsn shtil. m'hot gornisht geredt.

00:26:03.396 --> 00:26:06.377
un hot oykhet ⟨ongerikht⟩ oykh gezungen.

00:26:06.703 --> 00:26:12.046
un MAYBE, er hot gekont. SOMETIME hobn zey nisht al- velekher yid hot nisht gekont in di heym davenen?

00:26:12.070 --> 00:26:13.633
do konen zey nisht.

00:26:14.179 --> 00:26:16.063
do kon er nisht, er shloft shoyn

00:26:16.626 --> 00:26:19.067
do kon er nisht keyn yidish vort.

00:26:23.292 --> 00:26:24.810
nu, vos

00:26:23.443 --> 00:26:27.369
volt ir gezogt az s'iz geven a gut lebn dort, in algemeyn?

00:26:28.118 --> 00:26:29.462
in algemeyn

00:26:28.135 --> 00:26:30.356
ven ir ze- ven ir zent geven a meydl.

00:26:30.312 --> 00:26:34.018
ver es hot gehat gute BUSINESS iz geven. nisht yeder hot gehat gut.

00:26:34.513 --> 00:26:36.515
s'iz geven oreme layt PLENTY.

00:26:36.235 --> 00:26:38.777
az far aykh, far ayer mishpokhe?

00:26:38.243 --> 00:26:40.616
⟨nu⟩, normal ⟨LIFE⟩

00:26:41.162 --> 00:26:43.518
nisht tsu groys, nisht tsu UNK.

00:26:43.677 --> 00:26:45.071
m'hot gemakht a lebn.

00:26:45.347 --> 00:26:48.091
ober ven m'hot zikh oyfgeefnt di BUSINESS

00:26:48.537 --> 00:26:50.961
konfektsye, demolt iz geganen.

00:26:52.030 --> 00:26:53.509
ganen UP, UP

00:26:53.852 --> 00:26:56.158
un m'hot shoyn genumen g- avek bahaltn

00:26:56.282 --> 00:26:57.620
futers

00:26:57.620 --> 00:26:59.684
di COLLARS, futers m'hot gekoyft.

00:27:00.214 --> 00:27:02.199
m'hot arayn⟨gegebn⟩ tsu goyim

00:27:02.442 --> 00:27:04.174
ikh kon dir zogn di nomen?

00:27:04.315 --> 00:27:05.439
di goyim?

00:27:04.348 --> 00:27:05.405
az ir vilt.

00:27:05.496 --> 00:27:06.738
⟨GRANICZNA⟩.

00:27:07.572 --> 00:27:09.163
hot men arayngegebn mantlen.

00:27:09.163 --> 00:27:13.347
tsu bahaltn. m'hot gevust, gemeynt m'vet tsurikkumen, m'vet alts hobn. ver hot gevust

00:27:13.347 --> 00:27:14.956
az m'vet ale oyshargenen?

00:27:15.368 --> 00:27:17.066
iz ven mayn shvester

00:27:17.106 --> 00:27:18.723
fun NEW YORK, Teme

00:27:18.723 --> 00:27:21.808
geblibn lebn, iz zi gekumen nokh Tshenstekhev

00:27:21.966 --> 00:27:24.764
hot zi geshribn a LETTER tsu di kristn.

00:27:24.764 --> 00:27:28.068
zi hot gehat a STORE, mit khazer

00:27:28.564 --> 00:27:30.650
veyst ⟨vos⟩ meynt khazer, fun di PIGS

00:27:31.095 --> 00:27:32.658
hot zi gehat a STORE

00:27:32.817 --> 00:27:36.948
hot zi geshribn tsun ir az ⟨er⟩ iz geblibn, un zi hot nisht vos ontsutun

00:27:36.948 --> 00:27:39.859
zol er shikn epes, hot tsun ir geshikt eyn mantl.

00:27:39.859 --> 00:27:42.598
m'hot arayngegebn f- efsher fuftsik mantlen tsun im

00:27:43.262 --> 00:27:45.157
hot tsun ir geshikt eyn mantl.

00:27:45.157 --> 00:27:46.193
UNK

00:27:46.637 --> 00:27:48.875
zi hot dokh nisht gevust tsi undz lebn mir.

00:27:49.287 --> 00:27:51.576
iz zi di ershte gekumen nokh Tshenstekhev.

00:27:51.987 --> 00:27:54.461
hot zi geshribn tsun ⟨im⟩, hot ⟨tsun ir⟩ geshikt a mantl.

00:27:56.172 --> 00:27:58.528
tsi iz Stashev geven modern?

00:27:58.956 --> 00:28:03.152
oh, geven an ⟨organizirte⟩ shtot, gelernte BOYS

00:28:03.225 --> 00:28:06.374
nisht do do, ⟨di⟩ loyfn, di vilde khayes.

00:28:06.702 --> 00:28:09.491
alts hot gehert tsu an organizatsye, ikh zog dir.

00:28:09.491 --> 00:28:10.731
POYLE TSIEN

00:28:10.731 --> 00:28:12.095
SHOMER HATSAIR

00:28:12.152 --> 00:28:14.559
SHOMER LEUMI, SHOMER DATI

00:28:14.667 --> 00:28:17.749
iz gevezn. bundistn zenen gevezn shoyn

00:28:17.822 --> 00:28:20.026
a bisl mer UNK ⟨zey⟩

00:28:19.830 --> 00:28:24.717
ikh hob aykh gemeynt tsi s'iz geven dortn elektrye un vaser?

00:28:24.943 --> 00:28:26.472
s'iz gevezn a sh-

00:28:25.585 --> 00:28:27.227
in, ineveynik

00:28:27.171 --> 00:28:28.734
vu? in di shtot?

00:28:27.227 --> 00:28:28.059
in

00:28:28.302 --> 00:28:29.207
yo

00:28:29.297 --> 00:28:34.370
a shva -CZARNA RZEKA hot zikh geven, fun a vaser adurkhgegangen. BEAUTIFUL vaser.

00:28:33.820 --> 00:28:39.028
ober ir hot ge- vaser hot gerint in hoyz? ⟨OR⟩ ir hot gehat do- dos hob ikh gemeynt.

00:28:36.790 --> 00:28:39.706
NO, NO, NO. m'hot gemuzt brengen vaser.

00:28:39.591 --> 00:28:40.783
fun vanet?

00:28:39.706 --> 00:28:41.795
mayn ma- fun di vaser.

00:28:42.173 --> 00:28:43.297
fun di zhike.

00:28:43.455 --> 00:28:46.385
s'iz adurkhgan a groyse zhike vayt

00:28:47.050 --> 00:28:49.372
un fun dem hot men ⟨getrogn⟩ vaser.

00:28:49.429 --> 00:28:53.451
es iz geven mener vos zey hobn gehat veser, hobn arayngegosn, un zey hobn

00:28:53.451 --> 00:28:55.363
gefirt tsu di mentshn.

00:28:55.133 --> 00:28:56.544
a vaser treger.

00:28:56.162 --> 00:28:58.636
a vaser tre- UNK veys, a vaser treger.

00:28:58.288 --> 00:29:00.189
un s'iz geven elektrye?

00:29:00.634 --> 00:29:02.400
elektrye shoyn gevezn.

00:29:02.575 --> 00:29:04.442
BEGINNING hot gehat lemp

00:29:04.515 --> 00:29:06.368
mit GAS. nakher

00:29:06.368 --> 00:29:08.166
nisht yeder hot gehat elektrye.

00:29:08.166 --> 00:29:10.028
a sakh hobn nokh nisht gehat keyn elektrye.

00:29:09.830 --> 00:29:10.910
ir hot gehat?

00:29:10.253 --> 00:29:12.761
oh, undz ho- m'hot ⟨dokh⟩ gedorfn naye

00:29:13.341 --> 00:29:17.250
⟨nokh⟩ gedorfn zen. yedes mol hot UNK dos gloz geplatst

00:29:17.425 --> 00:29:20.712
un azoy vi s'iz gevorn elektrye hot men di ershte gemakht elektrye.
